			Phase E.1 (2026-05-30): skip the Vue 3 SPA build during local
			Maven iteration with `mvn package -DskipSpa=true`. Default
			false so `mvn package` produces a complete WAR. The Frontend
			Maven Plugin downloads Node + pnpm into target/spa-tooling
			the first time it runs (~30 MB, cached for subsequent runs).
		-->
